---
description: Suggest project rules when repeated corrections reveal stable team conventions.
alwaysApply: true
---

- Suggest a rule only after repeated correction patterns, not on first mention.
- Propose focused, single-concern rules with clear scope.
- Check for existing related rules before proposing a new one.
- Frame rule suggestions as optional, helpful workflow improvements.
- Avoid repetitive or spammy rule suggestions in the same conversation.
